data.description: Backing to foothills, this elegant residence offers sweeping views of the Owyhees and a grand-scale footprint. Commanding attention with its regal curb appeal, the home resides on a quiet cul-de-sac street with nearby access to hiking trails. Pride of ownership is made evident within the beautifully maintained interior, remodeled with both form and function in mind. Formal living and dining spaces adorned in plantation shutters and picture windows provide elegant areas for hosting. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with premier stainless steel appliances, gorgeous quartz countertops, and crisp white cabinetry. New interior paint and beautiful hardwood floors create a refined elegance throughout the home. Set on the main-level, the primary retreat exudes luxury, featuring a remodeled en suite bathroom with a fully-tiled walk-in shower, a dual-sink vanity, and a Japanese soaker tub. The dual-sided walk-in closet has convenient access to the laundry room.
